title: The Heather-Moon
author: Williamson, C. N. (Charles Norris)
snippet: Rode four miles to Enterkinfootand made a call: thence three miles to Slunkerford with another call:thence six miles to Sanquhar, where there were twenty official visits tobe made: thence two miles to Whitehall, with two more calls: and areturn journey to Sanquhar, finishing the day's work at seven in theevening."
